KUQHUME iqupha epulazini elisendaweni yaseRobertson eKapa ngesikhathi abokufika baseLesotho belwa nabokufika baseZimbabwe bebanga imisebenzi yasemapulazini. Okhulumela amaphoyisa esifundazweni iWestern Cape, uCaptain FC Van Wyk, uthe ingxabano iqale ngo-5 ekuseni lezi zinhlangothi zombili zibanga amathuba emisebenzi emapulazini. “Kuthiwa abaseLesotho basola abaseZimbabwe ngokubathathela imisebenzi emapulazini,” kusho uVan Wyk. Abazibonele ngawabo bathi balinganiselwa ku-20 abantu abalimele, kwashiswa imijondolo. UVan Wyk uthi amaphoyisa aphenya icala lodlame emphakathini kodwa akukaboshwa muntu.